title: 07/12/21 DPS Hour 1 Michael Wilbon
itunes:title: 07/12/21 DPS Hour 1 Michael Wilbon
description:
Michael Wilbon talks to Dan about his frustration with the Milwaukee Bucks. Michael says he does not need to see Giannis Antetokounmpo do any more than he already is. Michael says that the Bucks can beat the Suns by playing inside the paint.
